name: ReliefValve
description: Prevents dangerous Steam buildups by letting you juggle games between library locations.

packageJSON.name: relief-valve
packageJSON.description: Juggle installed Steam games between locations.

scripts.compile: npm run clean && mkdir out && npm run js && npm run css && npm run html
scripts.js: npm run js:build && npm run js:vendor
scripts.html: npm run html:index && npm run html:client-templates
scripts.test: npm run lint && npm run test:run && npm run test:coverage
scripts.lint: npm run lint:js && npm run lint:css
scripts.start: npm run compile && npm run exec
scripts.watch: npm run compile && wr --exec "npm run compile" src
scripts.dist: npm run dist:src && npm run dist:all
scripts.dist:src: mkdir dist && cd dist && mkdir src && npm run dist:src:copy && npm run dist:src:install
scripts.dist:src:copy: npm run dist:src:copy:assets && npm run dist:src:copy:out && npm run dist:src:copy:package
scripts.dist:src:install: cd dist && cd src && npm install --production
scripts.build: npm run compile && npm run dist && npm run build:run

releases.name: Relief Valve v1.2.0
releases.body:
**Implemented enhancements:**
- **Dismiss warning about Steam being open if Steam quits** [#30](https://github.com/mathphreak/ReliefValve/issues/30)

releases.name: Relief Valve v1.1.0
releases.body:
**Implemented enhancements:**
- Improve error message if appmanifest file is invalid
- Handle changes to Steam file format slightly better
- Only show categories that have games installed #127
- Move links from `code.mathphreak.me` to `www.matthorn.tech`

**Development-related changes:**
- Moved from CoffeeScript to ES6/Babel
- Switched from Gulp to NPM scripts

releases.name: Relief Valve v1.0.0
releases.body:
It's 1.0 time! :tada:

**Implemented enhancements:**
- Handle Windows junction points slightly better [#117](https://github.com/mathphreak/ReliefValve/issues/117)
